## Example Usage

```r
library(moodDispensery)

# Example dataset
df <- data.frame(
  text = c(
    "I love this product",
    "This is terrible and frustrating",
    "It's okay, nothing special"
  )
)

# Run full analysis
result <- analyze_mood(df)

# View detailed results
result$detailed

# View summary
result$summary
```
